      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIGER TAILS (4) has been out of the placings at her last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (22.96) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has the ability and expected to go close. DAISY'S CHARM (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a third place finish (23.25) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Must be included in calculations. ZIPPING BERKELEY (7) was in winning form two back (19.85) at Gunnedah but ran below best last time at this track, finishing 8th. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. SOFT WHISPER (2) is always a threat when she draws this box.",
